{"tid":1658284,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民陣召集人岑子杰再度遇襲 旺角街頭遭鐵鎚扑頭重創","createTime":"2019-10-16T12:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T06:26:14.000Z","uid":3189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c82acb00faadd1d71298b36cabbdd97812be1db9","tid":1658284,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:42:46.000Z","msg":"民陣召集人岑子杰再次遇襲，晚上7時許，據報岑子杰於旺角雅蘭里福強工業大廈對開，突遭4至5名南亞裔蒙面男子持鐵鎚伏擊，他走避不及頭部被扑中受傷，當場血流如注癱在地上。警方表示，接報指上址有人打交，警員趕至時發現一名男傷者，召救護車將其送往廣華醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，民陣今晚在雅蘭里福強工業大廈開周年大會，並商討有關10月20日民陣九龍大遊行事宜，懷疑兇徒在上址埋伏施襲。民陣強烈譴責兇徒行為，事件更難免令人聯想到有人想阻嚇星期日民陣大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》翻查資料，民陣召集人岑子杰早於8月29日與朋友於佐敦德興街一間餐廳內被人以鐵通及棍球棒襲撃，岑子杰未有受傷，但其友人擋下兇徒三棍致左臂嚴重瘀腫，需送院治理。事後有車cam拍下兇徒施襲前後情況，清楚見到兩名兇徒乘坐白色Mark X私家車抵達現場，不足一分鐘內完成施襲，再乘坐白色私家車逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n一個半月兩度遇襲的岑子杰，已報名參選今屆區議會選舉，與同屬社民連的梁國雄及曾健成分別挑戰建議派。岑循沙田瀝源選區出選，該區現任區議員是公民力量成員黃宇翰。岑以「五大訴求，缺一不可；踢走暴政，全民表態」為參選宣言，表示港人看到港府於10月1日趕盡殺絕，警員向青年開槍，無不感到痛苦，而特首林鄭月娥引用緊急法訂立《禁止蒙面規例》，向港人下戰書，認為區選是在反送運動中開啟了選舉此一戰場，希望港人反抗到底。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191016/large/1571227789_42bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571227789_42bc.jpg&h=f7bca6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑子杰滿面鮮血，倒卧路中心。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191016/large/1571227880_77a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571227880_77a5.jpg&h=f1ae0461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑子杰走避不及頭部被扑中受傷，當場血流如注癱在地上。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191016/large/1571227880_e0bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571227880_e0bd.jpg&h=93a1b460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方到場調查。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191016/large/1571227880_89df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571227880_89df.jpg&h=eda1717e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場遺下大灘血迹。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191016/large/1571228073_1739.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571228073_1739.jpg&h=b82dc118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月29日，持球棒（灰衣）及鐵通（黑衣）的蒙面兇徒衝入餐廳施襲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191016/large/1571228073_41a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571228073_41a5.jpg&h=cf6f61a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前岑子杰友人曾替他擋下兇徒三棍致左臂嚴重瘀腫，需送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191016/60161814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F60161814&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=253343bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F60161814&h=5a45c42e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191016/60161814</a>"},{"pid":"778a0e484181e8ff1c5e0b84161e6aac58b61dd8","tid":1658284,"uid":12469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa299bf15ab4ba7f7996633b9e62b880def54c9c","tid":1658284,"uid":24160,"lik