href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1658238/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1658238/page/1</a><br />\n「邊個呃人」"},{"pid":"bf23956aba4bb584e4b2076da86eb045ae72baad","tid":1658284,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:25:41.000Z","msg":"終於明白 襲擊子杰【真正目的】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659465</a>"},{"pid":"83fbc0be38614152d4ef3280def69e52220f1273","tid":1658284,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"終於明白 襲擊子杰【真正目的】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659465</a>"}]}